data.title: Medicine
data.meta_description: cv - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Baha Ghaleb Albaradiyah is a physician from Hebron, Palestine seeking a challenging role utilizing his medical and management skills. He has a Bachelor's Degree in Doctor of Medicine from the University of Jordan. His work experience includes serving as a physician at Al-Makased Hospital in Jerusalem from May 2021 to November 2021. He has strong personal skills including the ability to work independently and as part of a team, as well as problem-solving, organizational, and analytical skills. He is fluent in English, German, and Arabic.
